    • associateConstructsTogether

      CodeFragment associateConstructsTogether(List<Map.Entry<String,Map<String,AssignedValue>>> variationPointConstructs, PositiveVariationPointCandidateTemplates selectedTemplate)
      Associated/synthesized the code constructs together under given code structures
      Parameters:
      variationPointConstructs - - the list of associated code constructs with selected variation point that can be aggregated under new code construct
      selectedTemplate - -to find used positive variability variation point where code should be aggregated and get relevant export locations of associated code constructs
